high_descs: Turn around and proceed through the first left doorway, then continue through the second left doorway, and come to a stop at the left-hand shelf.
Pick up the banana on the shelf that's under the lemon.
Turn around and head towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the banana on the left side of the middle shelf, close the fridge, open the fridge, and remove the banana once more.
Turn right, cross the room, enter the left doorway, and continue through another left doorway, heading to the sink.
Place the banana in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Taking a banana from a shelf, placing it in the fridge, removing it, and ultimately placing it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around move few step then turn left, move forward and turn left, walk to the shelf to your left
Pick up the banana from the rack.
Turn around and go to the fridge to your right.
Put the banana into the refrigerator and wait a few seconds, then pick it back up.
Turn right, head toward to the sink and turn left move forward then take left.
Put the banana on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Banana into the Sink

high_descs: Turn around and head left to reach the shelf.
Pick up the banana from the shelf.
Turn around to reach the fridge across the room.
Cool the banana in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to walk across the room and turn left to enter the bathroom to reach the sink.
Put the banana in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled banana in the sink.
